column2: Armed standoff on I-95 in Massachusetts: peacefully resolved
column5: Here is a developing story: armed standoff blocking I95 up here in Mass. Group of armed men in the woods.   whdh.com/… The MSP are actively working the situation.  twitter.com/…  Posting from my mobile so apologies for the garbage format.  Update: This is not your normal armed group. They identify as Rise of the Moors on YouTube.  All 9 men have been peacefully detained.
